high_descs: pick up the dirty rag on the left
turn around, and go to the far sink, and turn to face the sink.
put the rag in the sink, rinse it off, and pick the it back up.
turn around to face the toilet, and then go to the toilet
put the clean cloth on top of the toilet
anns.task_desc: put a clean cloth on top of the toilet

high_descs: Begin walking to the bathroom sink, then hang a left and walk up to the tub.
Take the left most dirty rag out of the tub.
Turn around and walk over to the sink most to the right.
Place the dirty rags in the sink basin most to the right and turn the water on , once the rags are clean turn the water off and pick the clean rags up.
Turn around and walk over to the toilet.
Place the clean rags on the farthest corner of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Place clean rags on the toilet tank.

high_descs: turn left from the sink to the bath tub
pick up the dirty shirt on the left that is in the bath tub
turn around and go back to the sink
put the dirty shirt in the sink and turn the water on, then take it out
turn left and walk towards the toilet
put the shirt on top of the toilet
anns.task_desc: Clean a dirty shirt using the sink
